    <title>R语言作业</title>
    <link href="https://wujackwill.github.io/2023/11/27/R%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A/"/>
    <id>https://wujackwill.github.io/2023/11/27/R%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A/</id>
    <published>2023-11-27T03:05:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-11-27T09:31:03.466Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-安装R语言和Rstudio"><a href="#1-安装R语言和Rstudio" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装R语言和Rstudio"></a>1. 安装R语言和Rstudio</h2><ol><li>安装R：进入r语言官网下载页面，点击<a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/CRAN/bin/windows/base/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download R for Windows</a>选择base，下载安装</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127103529.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>安装Rsutdio： 进入下载页面<a href="https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/，选择[Download" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/，选择[Download</a> RStudio Desktop for windows](<a href="https://download1.rstudio.org/electron/windows/RStudio-2023.09.1-494.exe)，下载安装" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://download1.rstudio.org/electron/windows/RStudio-2023.09.1-494.exe)，下载安装</a></li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127101048.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><h2 id="2-安装bibliometrix"><a href="#2-安装bibliometrix" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装bibliometrix"></a>2. 安装bibliometrix</h2><ol><li>打开Rstudio，点击file，New file, R script</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127101301.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>复制以下代码，粘贴到Rstudio</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">install.packages(&quot;bibliometrix&quot;, dependecies &#x3D; true) #安装bibliometrix</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">library(bibliometrix) # 导入bibliometrix包</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">biblioshiny() #导入程序</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>鼠标指针移动到第一行，点击Run逐行运行代码,出现下载的程序包在….证明安装成功</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127101534.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>三行代买运行完，如果浏览器弹出下图，则安装成功</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231126222152.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>最后，将文件保存到桌面</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127101750.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>输入文件名，点击确定</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127101900.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><h2 id="3-导入web-of-science文献"><a href="#3-导入web-of-science文献" class="headerlink" title="3. 导入web of science文献"></a>3. 导入web of science文献</h2><ol><li>登入学校wos网站或者别的图书馆资源</li><li><strong>database一定选择web of science core collection</strong>，不然不能导出bibtex格式</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127104607.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>输入主题，开始检索，导出为bibtex格式</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127104134.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127100352.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><p><em>左侧Refine results可以调整搜索结果，按自己研究筛选结果</em></p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127104226.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><p><em>以只要2023年研究为例，点击Publication Years中的2023，再点击Refine即可</em></p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127104420.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>一次只能导出50个结果，第一次导出1-50，第二次51-100，以此类推，记得每次勾选full record and cited references</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127100548.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>一个bibtex即可导入，如有多个，将bib文件全部压缩为zip压缩包一起导入到biblioshiny</li></ol><h2 id="4-biblioshiny做图"><a href="#4-biblioshiny做图" class="headerlink" title="4. biblioshiny做图"></a>4. biblioshiny做图</h2><h3 id="4-1-导入数据"><a href="#4-1-导入数据" class="headerlink" title="4.1. 导入数据"></a>4.1. 导入数据</h3><ol><li>依次选择左侧按钮Data，Import raw file(s)，Web of Science (WoS/WoK)，最后点击Broswe选择文件</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127103128.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li><p>选择一个bib文件或者zip文件，点击打开</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127102246.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure></li><li><p>以zip文件为例，点击start</p></li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127102346.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>导入成功，点击close<figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127102602.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure></li></ol><h3 id="4-2-做图"><a href="#4-2-做图" class="headerlink" title="4.2 做图"></a>4.2 做图</h3><p>以论文中此图为例</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127102753.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>依次点击，生成图片</li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127102906.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>点击图表，下载图片，<strong>有的图片直接点击会卡死，如果卡死，重新运行代码、导入数据，直接截图就行</strong></li></ol><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="/images/R语言作业/Pasted%20image%2020231127102943.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><ol><li>照着范文，修改为自己的内容、数据，最后调整论文格式</li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;1-安装R语言和Rstudio&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-安装R语言和Rstudio&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1. 安装R语言和Rstudio&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. 安装R语言和Rstudio&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;安装R：进入r语言官</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
